    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Bokermannohyla (Anura: Hylidae) from highlands of Central Brazil" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213547>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213548>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213549>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213550>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213551>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213552> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213547>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. (A) Holotype of Bokermannohyla sapiranga (CHUNB 62384). (B) Adult male of Bokermannohyla pseudopseudis from the Parque Nacional da Chapada dos Veadeiros Goiás State, Brazil. Photos by Reuber Brandão." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/213547/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213548>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Holotype of Bokermannohyla sapiranga (CHUNB 62384): Dorsal body view (A); head profile (B); ventral surface of hand and forearm (C); ventral body view (D); ventral surface of foot and shank (E). Photos by Leandro Campos." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/213548/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213549>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution of Bokermannohyla pseudopseudis and Bokermannohyla sapiranga in the two first principal components using morphometric variables selected by Akaike Selection Criterion (B. pseudopseudis: male (․), female (□), and young (half square); B. sapiranga: male (●), female (Ο), and young (half circle)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/213549/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213550>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Call of Bokermannohyla sapiranga from Brasília Municipality, Distrito Federal (type locality): waveform (A); audiospectogam (B); and powerspectrum (C). Recording by Rubens Hisanari Matsushita (December 11, 2004; 21: 00 h; air temperature, 19.9 ºC; air humidity, 75 %)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/213550/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213551>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Type locality (black star) and geographical records (black circles) of Bokermannohyla sapiranga and Bokermannohyla pseudopseudis (dot center circles). Map by Renata Françoso-Brandão." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/213551/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.213552>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Basking behavior of Bokermannohyla sapiranga juvenile in a pebble beach of Barão rivulet, Poço Azul, Brasília, Distrito Federal in 23 October 1994, 16: 00 hs." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/213552/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

